																		<h2 class="entry-title fusion-post-title fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" data-fontsize="24" data-lineheight="35.04px" style="--fontSize:24; line-height: 1.46; --minFontSize:24;">Machines: Gears</h2>							
														<div class="fusion-flexslider flexslider fusion-flexslider-loading post-slideshow fusion-post-slideshow">
